data.description: *****ATTENTION!!!! The washer, dryer, and black refrigerator is included******The house is wired for a generator use. This home is positioned across the street from a charming park with a splash pad and walking trail, perfect for the outdoor enthusiast, in a quiet, well designed subdivision of Freeman Ranch. This house offers 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. One bedroom can be used as Study/Formal Dining. Entertain your guest in a spacious family room, just off the open flow of the kitchen, completed with granite counter tops or relax in your king-sized Primary suite with a spacious tub and separate shower. Enjoy cookouts, birthdays and holidays in the fully fenced backyard, engineered with a magnificent concrete slab that hugs the home, while sitting under the covered patio, hiding you from the Texas heat. 10 minutes away from Katy Mills mall and many restaurants. Once you step foot inside, it just feels like home. Come see for yourself.
